$f(x) = e^x$: $f(0) = e^0 = 1$
$f'(x) = e^x$: $f'(0) = e^0 = 1$
$f''(x) = e^x$: $f''(0) = e^0 = 1$
$f'''(x) = e^x$: $f'''(0) = e^0 = 1$
